# Four platform archetypes require fundamentally different strategies
@type: comparison

@compare:
  header: Archetype | Core Asset | Key Metric | Winner-Takes-Most?
  row: Transaction Platforms | Matching efficiency (buyers/sellers) | GMV, take rate | Yes — strong network effects
  row: Content Platforms | Creator ecosystem + catalog | MAU, engagement time | Moderate — taste matters
  row: Data Platforms | Proprietary signal aggregation | Data richness, query latency | Yes — data moats compound
  row: Infrastructure Platforms | Developer tools + APIs | Developer count, API calls | Yes — switching costs high

