# The three-phase playbook for platform launch and scale
@type: timeline

@step: Phase 1 (0–12 months) | Seed the Core | Recruit anchor suppliers, subsidize early demand, achieve liquidity in 1 geography
@step: Phase 2 (12–30 months) | Expand the Network | Geographic rollout, adjacent supply categories, demand-side growth loops
@step: Phase 3 (30–60 months) | Monetize and Defend | Raise take rate, launch data monetization, build switching cost moat

@source: BCG Platform Launch Playbook, based on 40+ platform launches, 2024

@notes: Phase 1 is almost always loss-making. Investors and boards need to understand that liquidity is the asset being built, not profit.

